# 🎧 Moodify Pro – Mood-Based Song Recommender

**Moodify Pro** is a smart, minimal, and feel-good music recommendation app built with **Python**, **TextBlob**, and **Streamlit**. Just type how you're feeling, and it will detect your mood using Natural Language Processing and recommend Bollywood songs accordingly! ❤️🎶

---

## 🌟 Features

- 🔍 Mood detection using sentiment analysis (TextBlob)
- 🎵 Song recommendations tailored to your emotion
- 🌘 Toggle between light & dark themes
- 🚀 Streamlit-powered UI (super fast & easy to deploy)
- 🎯 Real-time updates without reloading

