---

## 🧠 How It Works

1. User enters how they feel in natural language.
2. TextBlob analyzes the polarity of the sentence.
3. Based on the mood (excited, sad, love, neutral, etc.), recommended songs are shown with clickable YouTube links.

---

## 📦 Requirements

Install the dependencies using:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt


direct clone and run 
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/moodify-pro.git
cd moodify-pro
